Package: Cellivista
Type: Package
Title: cellivista: An Interactive Seurat Based Shiny App for Single Cell RNA seq Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Arnoneel", family = "Sinha", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "arsinha@augusta.edu")
Description: A Shiny application for end-to-end single-cell RNA-seq analysis using Seurat,
    including quality control, post-QC filtering, doublet removal, sample integration,
    downstream clustering and UMAP visualization, cluster-wise DGEA, annotation,
    and gene-level FeaturePlot generation.
